N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 454.11 - Resale of electric power and energy

State Regulations

Unless otherwise provided in the applicable service tariff, or other contract documents, customer shall not sell any of the electric power
and energy delivered to it under this Part, except to such purchaser(s) and
upon such terms and at such rates as the authority shall
approve. Notes
